answer: The Guide titled "iqr/08.-iqr_reference-guide_submission-requirements_august_vfinal_508.pdf" published in August 2025 is the official source with data requirements for the 2025 fiscal year under the Hospital Inpatient Quality Reporting Program, requiring quarterly data submissions including HCAHPS, SEP-1, and other selected clinical process measures for the calendar year (CY) 2025 reporting period.
